title: Salgótarjáni BTC
text:
Salgótarjáni Barátok Torna Club is a <a href="Hungary">Hungarian</a> <a href="Football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club from the town of <a href="Salg%C3%B3tarj%C3%A1n">Salgótarján</a>.
History.
Salgótarjáni Barátok Torna Club debuted in the <a href="1935-36%20Nemzeti%20Bajnoks%C3%A1g%20I">1935–36</a> season of the <a href="Hungarian%20League">Hungarian League</a> and finished third.
